pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: eng-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 60, 400, 24]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>THREE ENGINES</p>

  - elementId: eng-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 90, 600, 50]
    content:
      style: "$title"
      fontSize: 36
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Three engines. Zero setup.</p>

  - elementId: eng-card1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [80, 180, 360, 440]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$secondary"}

  - elementId: eng-card1-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [110, 210, 40, 40]
    iconName: "fas:bolt"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: eng-card1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [110, 270, 300, 36]
    content:
      fontFamily: "HedvigLettersSans"
      fontSize: 28
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Rules Engine</p>

  - elementId: eng-card1-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [110, 320, 300, 260]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 18
      lineHeight: 1.7
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Instant simulation via 55 personality trait mappings. <span style="color:$primary;">Zero download. Zero API key.</span> Fully offline in any browser.</p>

  - elementId: eng-card2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [460, 180, 360, 440]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$secondary"}

  - elementId: eng-card2-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [490, 210, 40, 40]
    iconName: "fas:microchip"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: eng-card2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [490, 270, 300, 36]
    content:
      fontFamily: "HedvigLettersSans"
      fontSize: 28
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Local AI</p>

  - elementId: eng-card2-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [490, 320, 300, 260]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 18
      lineHeight: 1.7
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Llama 3.2 runs inside your browser via WebLLM and WebGPU.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px"><span style="color:$primary;">One-time 600MB download. Then fully offline.</span></p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px">No data leaves your device. No API costs.</p>

  - elementId: eng-card3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [840, 180, 360, 440]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$secondary"}

  - elementId: eng-card3-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [870, 210, 40, 40]
    iconName: "fas:cloud"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: eng-card3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [870, 270, 300, 36]
    content:
      fontFamily: "HedvigLettersSans"
      fontSize: 28
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Claude API</p>

  - elementId: eng-card3-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [870, 320, 300, 260]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 18
      lineHeight: 1.7
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Anthropic's Claude Sonnet for maximum realism and depth.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px"><span style="color:$primary;">Bring your own key. Premium quality.</span></p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px">Richer in-character responses, deeper strategic analysis.</p>

  - elementId: eng-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [80, 680, 1120, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$primary"}

  - elementId: eng-brand
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1020, 688, 180, 22]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      fontSize: 11
      letterSpacing: 2
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>THE WAR ROOM</p>